text: The 2016 Icelandic Women's Football Cup, also known as Borgunarbikar kvenna for sponsorship reasons, was the 36th edition of the Icelandic national football cup. ==Calendar== Below are the dates for each round as given by the official schedule: {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" !
